{"tid":1912703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（自私撚）食客將口罩放筷子筒上","createTime":"2020-03-06T09:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T10:09:23.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a52acbdc3ab450eaf099a0d9120e3e7917e2be22","tid":1912703,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ct8Xn7k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fct8Xn7k.png&h=7a755988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐，食肆亦加強戒備，有茶記在卡位及圓枱設透明膠板，防止「對食」客人飛沫互傳，惟客人亦有責任注意個人衞生。昨晚一張男子在食肆被偷拍相在網上瘋傳，相中男子一邊低頭玩手機一邊開餐，疑是用過的口罩就放在旁邊的筷子筒上，如晾曬被鋪一樣，網民擔心令筷子有機會沾上事主的唾液。"},{"pid":"8ce3f9e03b0722c60b40f3ba2d511b78357a8070","tid":1912703,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200306/HFSS622POSU25UYDZA72CTTHYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200306%2FHFSS622POSU25UYDZA72CTTHYI%2F&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcAogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=08b79833\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200306%2FHFSS622POSU25UYDZA72CTTHYI%2F&h=0b5ee744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200306/HFSS622POSU25UYDZA72CTTHYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n全文：蘋果日報"},{"pid":"e99ea6cfa371de11d6c089d4e05076510af1e947","tid":1912703,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:19:56.000Z","msg":"(代po) 【突發】推介港台/Viutv節目嘅Instagram上線啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1912701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1912701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fae2737f591c8fbd98bd33e3c50432062df8cad3","tid":1912703,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oReSWuE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoReSWuE.jp